OL,5, The BBC was under "huge pressure" to   
OL,6, reveal that Huw Edwards was the        
OL,7, presenter facing media allegations last
OL,8, week, its acting chairwoman has said.  
OL,10,FA Sun story about an unnamed presenter 
OL,11,Fwho had allegedly paid a teenager for  
OL,12,Fexplicit photos sparked a media storm. 
OL,14,FThe BBC board held two emergency       
OL,15,Fmeetings in the next two days, acting  
OL,16,Fchair Dame Elan Closs Stephens said.   
OL,18,F"We had a duty to act with some calm   
OL,19,Fand rationality in the face of lack of 
OL,20,Frationality and lack of calm."         
